WEBVTT

00:09.200 --> 00:10.520
This is the permit to take the ship.

00:10.600 --> 00:11.720
Go.

00:12.480 --> 00:14.000
I won't drag you into this again.

00:18.160 --> 00:19.800
Let's never see each other again.

00:39.600 --> 00:41.280
You've cast loyalty aside,
but what about filial piety?

00:42.200 --> 00:44.760
You're drowning yourself
in sorrow and torment.

00:45.360 --> 00:47.000
Will His Grace rest in peace knowing this?

00:48.480 --> 00:50.200
The dead are like extinguished lamps.

00:51.720 --> 00:53.080
He wouldn't know anymore.

00:56.200 --> 00:57.080
You're not as good as him.

00:58.160 --> 00:59.360
No, I'm not.

01:16.200 --> 01:17.040
Your Grace,

01:17.120 --> 01:18.600
NOBLE SPIRIT CHASES THE CLOUDS
HEROIC SOULS LIVE FOREVER

01:18.680 --> 01:21.000
you were the Grand General
of Futing's army and its people.

01:21.080 --> 01:24.160
The comfort and prosperity I've enjoyed

01:24.840 --> 01:26.080
are thanks to you.

01:27.040 --> 01:28.760
You fought with your life

01:29.320 --> 01:30.320
to protect Futing's lands

01:31.400 --> 01:33.240
and bring peace to its people.

01:34.280 --> 01:35.160
Thank you.

01:35.680 --> 01:36.720
May you rest in peace.

01:38.920 --> 01:41.800
His Majesty has killed the witnesses
and closed the case with a decree.

01:42.640 --> 01:45.120
If I don't overthrow the throne,
how else can I change any of this?

01:50.840 --> 01:53.280
Are your eyes only used to interrogate me?

01:54.560 --> 01:56.240
If His Majesty really wanted
to frame the Duke of Ding,

01:56.920 --> 01:59.480
would he have spared the Jiang family
just because of a ruler?

02:00.360 --> 02:01.320
Trust me,

02:01.840 --> 02:03.600
His Majesty knows the truth.

02:04.120 --> 02:06.480
He only closed the case
because the circumstances forced his hand.

02:10.800 --> 02:12.400
And I'm just supposed to swallow
my shame and hatred,

02:12.480 --> 02:14.240
return to court, and climb
the ranks like nothing happened?

02:14.880 --> 02:16.840
You've spent years away from the capital.

02:17.360 --> 02:19.000
You don't know much about
the current political landscape.

02:19.520 --> 02:20.720
How can you hope to overturn the case

02:20.800 --> 02:22.160
when the enemy hides in the shadows
and you're completely exposed?

02:22.920 --> 02:24.440
Right now, not only are all leads cut off,

02:25.040 --> 02:27.640
but your ambition, resolve,
and very nature

02:27.720 --> 02:28.560
are known throughout the court.

02:28.640 --> 02:30.720
You're like an unsheathed blade,

02:30.800 --> 02:32.040
its sharpness glaringly
obvious for all to see.

02:33.240 --> 02:34.560
Don't you see?
The true strength of a blade

02:34.640 --> 02:36.160
isn't in striking, but in restraint.

02:36.760 --> 02:39.000
Only by sheathing the blade,

02:39.080 --> 02:40.640
by concealing your edge,

02:40.720 --> 02:42.760
can you observe the bigger picture

02:42.840 --> 02:44.800
and decide your next move with clarity.

03:01.280 --> 03:02.880
the Duke of Ding fought hard with his life

03:03.760 --> 03:05.600
to protect Futing's lands

03:06.120 --> 03:07.120
and ensure peace for its people.

03:07.200 --> 03:09.800
He doesn't live on just in your heart,

03:10.400 --> 03:12.520
he lives in the hearts
of everyone in Futing.

03:13.400 --> 03:14.720
Everything you say,

03:15.240 --> 03:16.240
every move you make,

03:16.760 --> 03:18.640
carries the legacy he passed on to you.

03:19.280 --> 03:21.680
Song Mo, listen to me,

03:22.720 --> 03:23.960
from this day forward,

03:24.480 --> 03:26.640
you are him.

05:07.080 --> 05:08.160
ADAPTED FROM THE NOVEL "BLOSSOM"
BY AUTHOR ZIZI FROM QIDIAN CHINESE WEBSITE

05:18.720 --> 05:19.920
My Lord, you're here!

05:23.280 --> 05:25.480
My Lord, I've gathered news

05:25.560 --> 05:27.080
from the palace regarding
the Duke of Ding.

05:30.640 --> 05:31.480
What did you hear?

05:32.240 --> 05:34.320
The eunuchs have been gossiping.

05:34.840 --> 05:37.360
They say His Majesty kept staring at
the broken ruler and muttering nonsense,

05:37.440 --> 05:39.200
tormented by restless dreams
night after night.

05:39.720 --> 05:41.600
The physicians and fortune-tellers
are being summoned more frequently.

05:41.680 --> 05:44.720
It seems His Majesty
feels guilty about you.

05:45.400 --> 05:46.920
Why not take advantage of it?

05:48.160 --> 05:50.200
Dou Zhao was right once again.

05:50.720 --> 05:52.160
If it wasn't for that broken ruler,

05:52.680 --> 05:54.720
the Jiang family might not
have been spared.

05:55.640 --> 05:57.000
But how did she know that His Majesty,

05:58.160 --> 05:59.960
despite his regret over
the Duke of Ding's unjust death,

06:00.040 --> 06:01.600
would still feel compelled
to close the case?

06:02.400 --> 06:04.040
Who could the mastermind possibly be,

06:04.560 --> 06:07.840
for even His Majesty to act against
his own conscience to protect them?

06:08.840 --> 06:10.240
In a game of cards,

06:10.840 --> 06:12.160
sometimes you have to lose a hand

06:12.680 --> 06:14.120
to save the round.

06:14.720 --> 06:17.040
For an emperor,
the stakes are much higher,

06:17.120 --> 06:20.760
it's the entire court, the entire realm.

06:21.280 --> 06:22.320
During the southeastern typhoon,

06:22.400 --> 06:25.600
His Majesty sent the Crown Prince to lead
the disaster relief and win public favor,

06:25.680 --> 06:28.320
but His Grace opposed it
and took charge himself.

06:28.840 --> 06:31.120
Could it be that His Grace's refusal
to support

06:31.200 --> 06:32.680
the Crown Prince provoked retaliation?

06:33.280 --> 06:34.800
Are you saying

06:35.960 --> 06:38.600
that His Majesty concealed the truth

06:39.240 --> 06:40.320
to protect the Crown Prince?

06:45.160 --> 06:46.480
When the Duke of Ding was
escorted to the capital,

06:47.400 --> 06:48.840
did the princes make any move?

06:48.920 --> 06:52.120
Only the Crown Prince
and Prince Qing came to ask about it.

06:52.200 --> 06:53.680
There were no other movements.

06:56.840 --> 06:59.240
My Lord, we've got a problem
at the Futing military camp!

07:08.000 --> 07:09.880
The General hasn't returned.
We can't disband.

07:09.960 --> 07:11.760
-That's right, we can't disband!
-We can't disband!

07:13.440 --> 07:15.640
The damned court killed the Grand General.

07:15.720 --> 07:17.040
Why should we remain loyal?

07:17.120 --> 07:19.000
Instead of enduring this humiliation…

07:19.080 --> 07:20.480
We might as well become bandits!

07:20.560 --> 07:22.000
-Yes!
-Yes!

07:22.080 --> 07:22.960
Let's become bandits!

07:23.040 --> 07:24.720
Let's become bandits!

07:24.800 --> 07:26.240
Such talk will get you executed.

07:26.320 --> 07:27.960
Don't ever say it again.

07:28.480 --> 07:30.640
-General!
-General!

07:30.720 --> 07:31.840
I've been stripped of my rank.

07:33.400 --> 07:34.360
I'm not your general anymore.

07:34.960 --> 07:36.320
I came to say goodbye.

07:36.960 --> 07:39.640
From now on, we go our separate ways

07:40.320 --> 07:41.480
and forge our own paths.

07:42.080 --> 07:44.160
General, we're soldiers.

07:44.240 --> 07:45.400
None of us fear death.

07:45.480 --> 07:47.240
Living as cowards,
with no clarity or justice,

07:47.320 --> 07:48.640
would disgrace the Grand General's spirit!

07:48.720 --> 07:50.520
We dream of avenging him!

07:50.600 --> 07:51.600
We'd gladly give our lives for it!

07:51.680 --> 07:54.200
If we knew who the murderer was,
we'd have exacted revenge!

07:54.280 --> 07:56.840
-General!
-General!

07:59.520 --> 08:01.800
If you still see me as your general,

08:02.880 --> 08:04.240
here's my order,

08:05.160 --> 08:08.200
the Duke of Ding's Army is disbanded,
effective immediately!

08:08.280 --> 08:09.360
-What?
-What?

08:09.440 --> 08:10.360
Disband?

08:10.440 --> 08:11.680
We can't disband.

08:11.760 --> 08:14.760
Officers ranked vice commander and above,
follow me to the tent for a council.

08:16.320 --> 08:18.120
-I'm not going anywhere.
-Me neither.

08:21.200 --> 08:23.240
You all have shown
unwavering loyalty to my uncle,

08:24.400 --> 08:26.080
so I will not deceive you.

08:27.440 --> 08:28.800
Though the imperial judgment
has been issued,

08:28.880 --> 08:30.040
the true mastermind remains at large.

08:31.040 --> 08:33.600
I intend to uncover the truth
and take vengeance on the real killer.

08:34.400 --> 08:35.799
This path will be fraught with danger.

08:36.320 --> 08:39.159
From now on, you can no longer
serve as soldiers in the open,

08:39.880 --> 08:40.840
but must serve as agents in the shadows.

08:43.520 --> 08:45.160
We knew you wouldn't abandon us!

08:46.280 --> 08:48.840
For over a decade, we've been
stationed at the border,

08:48.920 --> 08:50.960
knowing little of the inner workings
of the court.

08:51.040 --> 08:52.720
That ignorance has left us
vulnerable to schemes time and again.

08:53.840 --> 08:56.360
Now, whether it's to overturn the case

08:56.880 --> 08:59.280
or preserve a remnant
of the Duke of Ding's Army,

08:59.800 --> 09:02.720
we must plant our eyes
and ears within the court.

09:04.320 --> 09:06.000
General, just give the orders.

09:06.080 --> 09:07.360
Bring the wine!

09:11.360 --> 09:12.960
A force of 50,000 is too conspicuous.

09:13.480 --> 09:15.800
Select the 500 most elite soldiers
to follow me to the capital.

09:16.440 --> 09:20.080
The rest will disperse as ordered,
laying low to preserve our strength

09:20.960 --> 09:23.520
until the time comes to rise again.

09:24.120 --> 09:26.200
The 53,000 soldiers of
the Duke of Ding's Army

09:26.280 --> 09:28.240
are ready to go through hell
and high water for this cause!

09:28.320 --> 09:31.160
Through hell and high water!

09:31.240 --> 09:32.680
-Drink!
-Drink!

09:51.200 --> 09:52.080
Stop fighting for it!

09:54.080 --> 09:55.760
-Stop fighting for it!
-We've just been released.

09:55.840 --> 09:57.400
-We're victims in this too.
-You…

09:57.480 --> 09:59.040
The charges of colluding with
the enemy have been cleared.

10:00.840 --> 10:02.600
What you're doing is outright robbery!

10:02.680 --> 10:05.600
-Don't take that away.
-Please don't take that away!

10:05.680 --> 10:06.640
Mrs. Liu!

10:06.720 --> 10:08.280
You only invested 10 taels,

10:08.360 --> 10:10.920
but this bag of jewelry and jade
is worth 50 or 60 taels!

10:11.000 --> 10:12.800
Your family didn't pay back
the money on time,

10:12.880 --> 10:13.840
don't we deserve a little interest?

10:14.440 --> 10:15.640
Move!

10:16.360 --> 10:17.720
Stop it!

10:18.680 --> 10:20.240
Don't take that away!

10:20.320 --> 10:21.200
According to the law,

10:22.400 --> 10:23.600
burglary is a serious crime.

10:23.680 --> 10:25.040
-Zhao.
-Even if you fail,

10:25.120 --> 10:26.240
it's 20 lashes and three years of exile.

10:27.120 --> 10:28.080
If you do succeed,

10:28.160 --> 10:30.280
you're looking at
either exile or the noose.

10:30.360 --> 10:33.000
And committing this in broad daylight?
That makes it even worse.

10:37.760 --> 10:39.680
They owe us money. Isn't it only
fair that we take what we're owed?

10:40.320 --> 10:42.040
Oh, is that so?

10:42.120 --> 10:43.240
Fair, you say?

10:43.760 --> 10:45.200
Is it also fair to smash things
and hurt people?

10:46.640 --> 10:47.520
Hurting someone?

10:47.600 --> 10:49.160
The punishment for that is even harsher.

10:49.880 --> 10:51.960
What choice do we have?

10:53.000 --> 10:56.440
Our goods rotted away
on those impounded ships.

10:56.520 --> 10:58.040
Everything we worked so hard for is gone!

10:58.560 --> 11:00.680
-That's right.
-Yes.

11:07.840 --> 11:10.680
I am Dou Zhao, a daughter of
the Dou family from the capital,

11:10.760 --> 11:12.800
and also the master of the Miao family.

11:13.520 --> 11:15.240
I will sign an agreement right now

11:15.320 --> 11:16.720
to settle this debt in ten days.

11:19.560 --> 11:21.640
This jade bracelet is a family heirloom,

11:22.240 --> 11:23.920
and I'll leave it
with the authorities as collateral.

11:24.440 --> 11:27.120
I'll pay you back in ten days.

11:29.480 --> 11:31.920
That's your mother's keepsake. You can't!

11:35.760 --> 11:36.640
If you trust me,

11:37.320 --> 11:38.560
sign the agreement.

11:39.160 --> 11:40.040
If not,

11:40.560 --> 11:42.000
come with me to the authorities.

11:42.080 --> 11:44.240
Let's see who owes more, the Miao family,

11:44.320 --> 11:46.760
or you all with your looting,
smashing, and injuries.

11:53.800 --> 11:55.560
-I'll sign.
-Me too.

11:57.760 --> 11:59.120
Me as well.

12:05.320 --> 12:06.160
HE YUE YE, LENG YUE YUN
JUN XUAN LING

12:11.080 --> 12:14.560
DOU ZHAO

12:18.280 --> 12:19.120
Hang in there.

12:22.960 --> 12:24.840
Luckily, the wound isn't deep.

12:27.120 --> 12:28.200
Zhao,

12:28.880 --> 12:31.200
I can't let you pawn
your bracelet for those people.

12:31.280 --> 12:33.480
You came all the way to Futing for me.

12:33.560 --> 12:34.840
I'm grateful to you.

12:34.920 --> 12:37.400
This is my burden to bear.

12:37.480 --> 12:38.760
I'll go to the pawn shop

12:38.840 --> 12:40.680
and sell the warehouse and store,

12:40.760 --> 12:41.880
whatever it takes
to get your bracelet back.

12:41.960 --> 12:44.040
Pawn shops wouldn't
recognize their true value.

12:44.560 --> 12:47.280
What's a store or warehouse
compared to you?

12:48.600 --> 12:51.080
Why don't you just pawn yourself
to me instead?

12:53.000 --> 12:54.480
That works too.

12:55.160 --> 12:56.920
At the going rate for a steward's wages,

12:57.000 --> 12:59.640
I'd need to work for you

13:00.160 --> 13:02.600
for 3,224 days.

13:03.200 --> 13:05.880
That's about eight or nine years,
it should be enough to pay it off.

13:06.720 --> 13:07.960
I'm kidding.

13:08.920 --> 13:11.880
If my mother knew her bracelet was
being put to such good use,

13:11.960 --> 13:13.400
she'd be thrilled.

13:14.000 --> 13:15.360
Don't worry about it.

13:15.440 --> 13:16.880
I'm the richest person in Zhending,

13:16.960 --> 13:18.840
do you really think
I can't get a bracelet back?

13:27.760 --> 13:30.040
Here it says the six-percent interest
was supposed to cover goods purchased,

13:30.120 --> 13:31.520
but the accounts don't add up.

13:32.040 --> 13:32.880
Where are the goods?

13:35.040 --> 13:38.280
I invested it as stock in a food shop.

13:39.640 --> 13:41.400
Investing in a food shop
during a famine year?

13:41.920 --> 13:43.240
Brilliant move,

13:43.320 --> 13:45.880
turning gold into dust.

13:46.480 --> 13:48.040
We still have An Su's dowry, don't we?

13:48.120 --> 13:49.200
You good-for-nothing!

13:49.280 --> 13:50.880
Stop eyeing your sister's dowry.

13:51.480 --> 13:53.200
She's of marrying age,

13:53.280 --> 13:55.840
how is she supposed
to get married without money?

13:56.360 --> 13:58.160
What about An Ping then?

13:58.240 --> 13:59.960
An Ping is sitting for
the imperial exam this year.

14:00.040 --> 14:00.960
Are you going to let him

14:01.040 --> 14:02.440
-beg his way there?
-I…

14:02.520 --> 14:05.800
If it means paying off the debt,
then so be it,

14:06.320 --> 14:07.480
dowry or no dowry.

14:08.080 --> 14:11.480
My dowry exists thanks to Zhao's kindness.

14:12.000 --> 14:13.320
And now I'll use it

14:13.400 --> 14:15.280
to settle the debt
and spare her from trouble.

14:17.960 --> 14:18.880
It's not just for An Ping.

14:18.960 --> 14:21.400
An Su, are you really fine with it?

14:22.520 --> 14:23.400
I'm not.

14:27.800 --> 14:28.760
Zhao.

14:30.240 --> 14:32.600
There's still a lot of goods on the ship.
Have you taken inventory?

14:33.640 --> 14:34.880
Things just settled down,

14:34.960 --> 14:36.720
and the local authorities
in Futing are still in chaos.

14:36.800 --> 14:38.800
I haven't had the chance to do it yet.

14:41.560 --> 14:43.680
DOU'S RESIDENCE

14:43.760 --> 14:44.920
Shi Shu,

14:45.000 --> 14:47.120
Ying Xue insisted

14:47.200 --> 14:48.560
I ask about Ming
and De Zhen's engagement.

14:49.160 --> 14:52.360
She said if we have
my father-in-law mediate,

14:52.880 --> 14:54.880
Grand Secretary Wu might agree.

15:01.080 --> 15:02.800
-A letter from Mu Chuan?
-He has just risen

15:02.880 --> 15:04.840
to the Grand Secretariat.

15:05.360 --> 15:07.560
Most of the old allies of the Duke of Ding
in the previous administration

15:08.080 --> 15:09.640
have retired to their hometowns.

15:09.720 --> 15:12.920
Wu Yi Fen is advanced in years.

15:13.440 --> 15:14.600
How much longer can he hold on?

15:17.080 --> 15:18.440
What are you trying to say?

15:19.320 --> 15:21.920
That faction's influence is fading fast.

15:22.000 --> 15:23.760
The Wu family's standing

15:24.560 --> 15:25.800
will inevitably collapse.

15:27.440 --> 15:29.480
Is there still a point to
forming ties with them?

15:30.960 --> 15:32.600
You should have Ying Xue focus on

15:33.480 --> 15:35.480
strengthening connections
with the Wei family instead.

15:37.560 --> 15:41.800
CUI'S RESIDENCE

15:47.520 --> 15:48.360
Come.

15:53.360 --> 15:55.360
Now that you've delivered the gifts,
you can go.

15:55.440 --> 15:58.080
If you stay longer and get sick,
you'll blame it on Shou Gu again.

15:59.880 --> 16:02.840
It's rude to kick people out
right after receiving gifts.

16:02.920 --> 16:04.720
Even if Young Lady Zhao
isn't up to seeing guests,

16:04.800 --> 16:08.240
she could at least say thank you.

16:09.920 --> 16:11.720
This is the Dou family's business.

16:11.800 --> 16:13.920
Shouldn't you consider your identity first

16:14.000 --> 16:16.680
if you want to meddle?

16:16.760 --> 16:19.160
-I'll have you know…
-Can I meddle then?

16:20.400 --> 16:21.560
Grandmother.

16:22.520 --> 16:25.840
You're causing trouble here
in broad daylight.

16:26.520 --> 16:27.640
In all these years,

16:27.720 --> 16:30.080
you've barely delivered gifts
during festivals.

16:30.160 --> 16:32.920
Now that both Shou Gu and I are unwell,

16:33.520 --> 16:35.120
what are you scheming?

16:36.200 --> 16:37.960
Mother, you've misunderstood.

16:38.040 --> 16:40.360
I heard that Zhao came down with smallpox,

16:40.440 --> 16:42.760
so I went to the temple
for a smallpox protection statue.

16:42.840 --> 16:44.800
This isn't like other gifts,

16:44.880 --> 16:48.240
it must be personally
enshrined by Zhao herself,

16:48.320 --> 16:50.600
-or it won't be effective.
-Alas.

16:51.160 --> 16:54.240
Guardian idols and deities?
I've never believed in these things.

16:54.320 --> 16:56.760
-Take it all away.
-That won't do, Mother.

16:56.840 --> 16:59.040
Inviting the gods is easy, but
sending them away is difficult.

16:59.120 --> 17:00.720
Neglecting the statue

17:00.800 --> 17:02.280
could harm the family's fortune.

17:02.360 --> 17:06.400
I'm sure Zhao wouldn't want
that to happen, would she?

17:07.160 --> 17:09.079
Young Lady Zhao, just show yourself…Ouch!

17:10.440 --> 17:11.560
Stop!

17:12.079 --> 17:14.839
Smallpox patients must avoid drafts.
Cover her up at once.

17:15.440 --> 17:16.440
Yes, Grandmother.

17:17.319 --> 17:19.240
Fine, I'll accept these gifts
on Shou Gu's behalf.

17:19.319 --> 17:21.720
I'm sure things are
busy for you in the capital,

17:21.800 --> 17:22.920
so I won't keep you.

17:23.000 --> 17:25.079
If there's nothing else, you should leave,

17:25.599 --> 17:27.640
and don't come back again.

17:28.240 --> 17:29.320
Old Madam,

17:29.400 --> 17:31.440
our mistress only came
with the best intentions.

17:31.520 --> 17:32.400
-What about…
-Nanny Zhou.

17:34.080 --> 17:37.960
Please pass the statue to Zhao, Mother.

17:38.040 --> 17:39.600
We'll take our leave now.

18:02.240 --> 18:03.960
-Move.
-Grandmother…

18:04.040 --> 18:04.880
Move!

18:10.360 --> 18:11.520
What's going on?

18:12.920 --> 18:14.320
Shou Gu…

18:14.840 --> 18:16.680
She went to freshen up.
She'll be back soon.

18:16.760 --> 18:19.080
At this point,
you can stop covering for her.

18:21.200 --> 18:23.240
Shou Gu is in Futing.

18:26.600 --> 18:28.240
Futing is a highly
sensitive area right now.

18:28.880 --> 18:30.080
What's she doing there?

18:30.160 --> 18:31.200
Does…

18:31.960 --> 18:34.200
Does she have something
to do with the case too?

18:34.280 --> 18:37.200
The Maritime Trade Office seized
the Miao family's merchant ship.

18:37.280 --> 18:40.880
Shou Gu was worried
about An Su going alone, so she…

18:42.760 --> 18:44.560
Ridiculous!

18:45.400 --> 18:48.480
-You girls… Absolutely ridiculous!
-All right now, all right.

18:48.560 --> 18:51.440
Madam, are we leaving already?
Shouldn't we take a closer look?

18:51.520 --> 18:52.760
Didn't you notice just now?

18:53.360 --> 18:55.320
That hand was smooth and flawless.

18:56.440 --> 18:59.760
If she really had smallpox,
how could there not be any rash?

19:00.280 --> 19:03.160
Our trip here wasn't wasted after all.

19:04.800 --> 19:06.360
Ah, I see.

19:06.440 --> 19:08.760
Let's go back to the capital.

19:09.320 --> 19:10.480
DOU'S RESIDENCE

19:10.560 --> 19:12.560
Zhao is brazen and reckless.

19:12.640 --> 19:14.480
As a young lady from a noble family,

19:14.560 --> 19:16.320
she not only shows her face in public,

19:16.400 --> 19:18.520
she even went to Futing on her own.

19:19.040 --> 19:23.240
Futing is in chaos right now
because of the Duke of Ding's case.

19:23.320 --> 19:25.840
I hear there have been outbreaks
of unrest among refugees lately.

19:25.920 --> 19:27.200
Oh, Zhao…

19:27.920 --> 19:29.320
Master, Madam,

19:29.400 --> 19:30.720
the Marquis of Jining's family

19:30.800 --> 19:33.520
has invited you both

19:33.600 --> 19:35.680
and the young ladies
to a banquet tomorrow.

19:35.760 --> 19:37.800
We can't possibly attend a banquet now.

19:37.880 --> 19:39.880
Since it's a specially arranged banquet,

19:39.960 --> 19:41.480
they might want to discuss the betrothal.

19:42.680 --> 19:45.360
Decline it. We'll talk about it
after I bring Shou Gu back.

19:45.880 --> 19:46.720
Someone, prepare the carriage.

19:47.680 --> 19:48.880
We mustn't decline it, my dear.

19:50.240 --> 19:53.240
If word that Zhao went to Futing gets out,

19:53.760 --> 19:57.760
it will ruin her marriage prospects
and Ming's too.

19:59.200 --> 20:01.440
How about we say

20:01.960 --> 20:03.680
you and the girls have caught a cold,

20:03.760 --> 20:04.880
and I'll attend the banquet alone?

20:07.720 --> 20:10.960
Fine, I'll leave it to you.
Handle it as you see fit.

20:11.040 --> 20:12.320
I should get going.

20:12.840 --> 20:13.760
Yes, my dear.

20:20.440 --> 20:22.000
This side dish is quite unique.

20:24.040 --> 20:25.400
Is it a specialty of Futing?

20:26.480 --> 20:27.840
I found a lot of spoiled food

20:27.920 --> 20:29.800
when we were clearing out the inventory.

20:29.880 --> 20:31.680
But there was a crate of tubers
from the West that hadn't gone bad.

20:31.760 --> 20:33.960
I roasted a few of them.

20:34.560 --> 20:36.800
They're soft, fragrant,

20:37.440 --> 20:38.560
and a bit like yams.

20:39.160 --> 20:40.720
But many of them have sprouted.

20:40.800 --> 20:42.960
We can't eat or sell them anymore.

20:44.120 --> 20:45.480
We can't eat them…

20:46.960 --> 20:48.080
But we can plant them!

20:49.880 --> 20:53.040
If they sprout even in the damp,
dark conditions of a ship's hold,

20:53.120 --> 20:54.560
they must be easy to grow.

20:56.080 --> 20:58.640
If you plant them now,

20:58.720 --> 21:00.480
you could have a harvest
in about three months.

21:01.880 --> 21:05.040
So, don't rush to repay me just yet.

21:05.120 --> 21:07.960
Use it to rent some unused land
and start planting.

21:08.040 --> 21:09.760
With all the floods this year,

21:09.840 --> 21:11.440
food is already in short supply.

21:11.960 --> 21:13.400
If you grow enough,

21:13.480 --> 21:14.920
not only will you feed people,

21:15.560 --> 21:18.680
but you'll also introduce a new food crop.

21:19.200 --> 21:20.440
No grain merchant would turn that away.

21:27.240 --> 21:29.520
At 50 coins per jin for white flour,

21:30.040 --> 21:32.560
one mu of land could
yield around 300 jin.

21:32.640 --> 21:34.800
With ten mu of land in a year,

21:34.880 --> 21:36.400
that's over a hundred taels of silver!

21:36.480 --> 21:38.160
That's a great idea.

21:38.240 --> 21:39.480
Let's do it your way.

21:40.080 --> 21:41.280
What good stuff do you have there?

21:42.880 --> 21:44.120
Ji Yong,

21:44.200 --> 21:45.200
you scared us again.

21:46.240 --> 21:47.480
You've got food here.

21:51.080 --> 21:52.560
-Try it.
-Here.

21:55.800 --> 21:58.200
Not bad. But it could be sweeter.

21:59.640 --> 22:02.080
Young Master Ji, why are you
wearing such a scary mask?

22:03.320 --> 22:05.440
It attracts fortune.
I'm here to bring you money.

22:07.000 --> 22:09.640
-You've made the deal? What's the price?
-Who's the buyer?

22:10.680 --> 22:12.720
Want to see it? Beg me.

22:16.440 --> 22:18.800
-Please.
-You actually begged?

22:19.560 --> 22:20.600
Well, that's no fun.

22:25.280 --> 22:26.320
Look.

22:28.560 --> 22:30.800
The Ministry of Works
is paying so much for the ship!

22:30.880 --> 22:33.280
The court has never
bought civilian ships before!

22:34.760 --> 22:37.160
If it weren't an unprecedented move,
I wouldn't have bothered.

22:37.760 --> 22:39.000
I submitted a proposal
to Minister Mu Chuan

22:39.080 --> 22:40.760
advocating for reforms
in maritime trade,

22:41.360 --> 22:42.840
selling civilian ships to the government

22:42.920 --> 22:44.800
and consolidating overseas trade
under the court's control.

22:45.640 --> 22:48.400
This way, we can ease people's burden
and replenish the national treasury.

22:50.560 --> 22:51.400
Thank you, Young Master Ji.

22:52.960 --> 22:56.320
No need to thank me. Mu Chuan only
agreed to see me because Dou Zhao

22:56.400 --> 22:58.000
sent the invitation
under the Dou family's name.

22:58.880 --> 23:01.360
-Zhao…
-No need for thanks between us.

23:02.600 --> 23:04.280
Now that the crisis is over,

23:04.360 --> 23:06.840
let's go back together tomorrow.

23:07.640 --> 23:08.720
Zhao,

23:09.680 --> 23:11.480
I can't go back with you.

23:12.760 --> 23:13.840
Every year during sailing season,

23:14.520 --> 23:16.480
I'd come here with my parents

23:16.560 --> 23:18.280
to oil and polish the ship.

23:18.360 --> 23:19.600
From a small boat to a big ship,

23:20.400 --> 23:21.880
now it's all gone in an instant.

23:23.320 --> 23:24.320
It's time for me to grow up.

23:26.040 --> 23:28.840
You're staying in Futing to
help with the family business?

23:29.800 --> 23:30.840
Zhao,

23:32.280 --> 23:33.680
I won't let you down.

23:35.160 --> 23:36.640
What I've lost today,

23:37.760 --> 23:38.920
I'll earn back in the future!

23:39.680 --> 23:40.520
All right!

23:41.640 --> 23:43.320
Let's wish for our hopes to come true,

23:43.400 --> 23:46.640
and for the days ahead to be
peaceful, free, and full of joy.

23:47.160 --> 23:48.880
Peaceful, free, and full of joy!

23:50.000 --> 23:51.040
Free, and full of joy!

23:59.160 --> 24:00.280
Greetings, Minister Mu.

24:02.120 --> 24:03.120
Greetings, Minister Mu.

24:04.120 --> 24:06.200
MINISTER OF WORK, MU CHUAN

24:07.360 --> 24:09.080
This way, please, My Lord.

24:20.920 --> 24:23.360
This idea of selling the ships
is priceless.

24:23.880 --> 24:25.440
I owe you a huge favor.

24:27.080 --> 24:28.920
What favor? It was just a game.

24:29.520 --> 24:32.080
The fun I had was worth
more than any fortune.

24:33.840 --> 24:35.240
Besides, I won Mu Chuan's favor
with the proposal.

24:35.320 --> 24:36.160
He submitted it to His Majesty
under his name.

24:36.240 --> 24:38.920
In return, he recommended
me for the position

24:39.440 --> 24:40.400
of secretary at the prince's residence.

24:41.080 --> 24:42.840
That role is low-ranking
and full of tedious responsibilities.

24:42.920 --> 24:45.000
You'd have to guide and advise the prince

24:45.080 --> 24:47.040
while also reporting regularly
to His Majesty.

24:47.120 --> 24:48.640
It's a thankless job that pleases no one.

24:49.480 --> 24:50.880
The harder the job,

24:50.960 --> 24:52.360
the easier it is to stand out.

24:52.880 --> 24:54.600
I prefer to work smart, not hard.

24:54.680 --> 24:57.120
I'm not about to let myself rot away
like those unsold goods on the ship.

24:57.200 --> 24:59.760
Since the Crown Prince isn't favored,

24:59.840 --> 25:00.920
I might as well take a bigger gamble

25:01.440 --> 25:02.920
and support another prince.

25:06.120 --> 25:08.520
You're going to Prince Qing's Residence?

25:10.440 --> 25:12.080
The Crown Prince's mother, Empress Shen,

25:12.160 --> 25:14.000
came from a humble background
and passed away early.

25:14.520 --> 25:16.120
He doesn't have many allies
among the court officials.

25:16.200 --> 25:18.240
Prince Qing, on the other hand,
is known for valuing talent,

25:18.320 --> 25:19.760
holds military power in Liaodong,

25:19.840 --> 25:21.920
and his mother, Empress Wan,
is favored by His Majesty.

25:22.000 --> 25:23.400
With me on his side,

25:23.480 --> 25:25.400
his chances of surpassing
the Crown Prince are much higher.

25:28.000 --> 25:30.320
I once heard that Prince Qing's
rebellion succeeded

25:31.080 --> 25:33.120
thanks to an extraordinarily
brilliant strategist by his side.

25:33.200 --> 25:34.560
JI YONG, PRODIGIOUS MONK

25:34.640 --> 25:35.480
Could it be him?

25:35.560 --> 25:36.600
A PRODIGY TO RIVAL WENCHANG,
DARING TO TEACH CONFUCIUS THE STARS.

25:36.680 --> 25:39.120
If Ji Yong goes to Liaodong
to assist Prince Qing,

25:39.720 --> 25:41.400
will he meet a tragic end again
because of it?

25:42.640 --> 25:43.640
I'd advise you

25:43.720 --> 25:45.000
to think it through carefully.

25:47.080 --> 25:48.680
I'll be straight with you.

25:49.760 --> 25:52.160
Prince Qing is rebellious,
he'll usurp the throne one day.

25:52.240 --> 25:53.840
Don't forget why you entered
officialdom in the first place.

25:56.520 --> 25:57.520
If he rebels,

25:58.040 --> 25:59.720
wouldn't that align perfectly
with my original intent?

26:07.480 --> 26:09.160
You've known all along…

26:09.760 --> 26:10.600
What happens in the future.

26:10.680 --> 26:14.560
Heaven knows, earth knows,
I know, and you know.

26:15.600 --> 26:16.960
I observe the world
without being controlled by it.

26:17.640 --> 26:19.800
Princes and kings, in my hands,

26:19.880 --> 26:20.760
are mere tools for a greater vision.

26:21.640 --> 26:23.200
The court is decayed,

26:24.040 --> 26:25.360
foreign enemies are poised to strike,

26:26.160 --> 26:29.120
and all I want is someone
who recognizes my worth

26:29.200 --> 26:30.480
and grants me the power to enact reform.

26:31.000 --> 26:33.240
Healing individuals is a small matter,

26:33.320 --> 26:34.480
healing a nation

26:34.560 --> 26:36.080
is where my true strategy lies.

26:36.160 --> 26:39.320
I can extend this dynasty's life
by a hundred years.

26:44.440 --> 26:46.560
Minister Mu, they're here.

26:53.280 --> 26:55.120
So, there are the tubers
you mentioned in your letter,

26:55.200 --> 26:56.800
the ones that don't spoil easily?

26:56.880 --> 26:58.920
The people of Futing call it a potato.

26:59.440 --> 27:02.440
Many of the other goods were
ruined after the delay,

27:02.520 --> 27:04.080
but these remained intact.

27:07.440 --> 27:08.840
Looks like this crop

27:09.800 --> 27:11.960
is far more valuable than

27:14.320 --> 27:15.840
the rest of the cargo on the ship.

27:16.480 --> 27:17.320
Here.

27:17.960 --> 27:19.000
TEA

27:19.080 --> 27:20.520
This strawberry ice cream

27:20.600 --> 27:22.240
is only available in Futing.

27:22.320 --> 27:24.280
Once I go to Liaodong,
there'll be no chance to have it.

27:24.800 --> 27:27.320
Didn't you say that ice cream
is too cold for the stomach

27:28.200 --> 27:30.240
and can make you feel lightheaded
if you eat too much?

27:30.320 --> 27:33.120
Silly. If you get sick,
I'll just treat you.

27:34.000 --> 27:35.120
Eat up.

27:36.200 --> 27:39.640
Real men drink wine and eat meat.

27:40.320 --> 27:42.200
Look at that grown man

27:42.280 --> 27:45.640
eating dainty sweets fit
for women and children.

27:46.400 --> 27:49.240
So now taste preferences
come with gender labels too?

27:49.320 --> 27:50.320
How childish.

27:51.280 --> 27:53.000
You two might drink and eat meat,

27:53.080 --> 27:54.840
but does it help you conquer battlefields

27:54.920 --> 27:56.280
or govern a nation?

27:57.960 --> 27:59.120
How arrogant!

27:59.200 --> 28:00.280
Young Lady,

28:00.360 --> 28:02.000
he's clearly not a suitable match!

28:03.520 --> 28:05.720
Right, unlike you two,
you're perfect for each other.

28:05.800 --> 28:07.000
You…

28:07.800 --> 28:09.520
Don't be mad. Let's drink.

28:10.040 --> 28:10.960
Drink.

28:12.640 --> 28:14.320
-Here.
-By the way,

28:16.480 --> 28:17.320
I got this for you.

28:19.160 --> 28:21.360
The snow in Liaodong is heavy,
and there are many hunting pits.

28:21.880 --> 28:24.040
I've noticed you always
squint when you look at things.

28:24.560 --> 28:25.640
I figured your eyesight isn't great.

28:26.520 --> 28:29.280
I went around the capital
and found this for you.

28:30.560 --> 28:32.480
Consider it a parting gift.

28:34.120 --> 28:35.400
You even noticed that?

28:48.400 --> 28:49.760
Looking up close now,

28:50.280 --> 28:51.880
you're actually not that ugly.

28:54.920 --> 28:56.680
All right, I'll give you
something in return.

28:57.760 --> 29:01.000
I always save the strawberry
on my ice cream for last

29:01.080 --> 29:02.480
because I can't bear
to eat them right away.

29:03.600 --> 29:04.640
I'll give it to you now.

29:10.000 --> 29:11.160
Shou Gu.

29:12.640 --> 29:13.920
Father?

29:14.000 --> 29:15.880
-Are you all right?
-What are you doing here?

29:15.960 --> 29:17.040
If we had come any later,

29:17.560 --> 29:19.600
you'd have probably turned
Futing upside down by now.

29:21.160 --> 29:23.280
-Uncle Shi Shu.
-You really are something.

29:23.360 --> 29:25.880
Disgracing the family
and running off to elope.

29:26.400 --> 29:28.720
You found yourself the perfect match, huh?

29:29.760 --> 29:30.960
Shou Gu,

29:31.040 --> 29:33.800
a young lady like you traveling
all the way to Futing on your own,

29:33.880 --> 29:35.360
do you know how worried we've been?

29:35.440 --> 29:37.680
Father, Uncle Shi Shu.

29:39.600 --> 29:42.360
This is Ji Yong, a cousin of
the Cui family from Jian'an.

29:42.880 --> 29:45.000
He's the official in charge
of the Maritime Trade Office's cases.

29:45.960 --> 29:47.440
Ah, so you're Master Ji's son.

29:48.200 --> 29:49.760
Greetings, uncles.

29:52.000 --> 29:54.640
You've truly gone to great lengths
to disgrace our family's name

29:54.720 --> 29:55.840
all the way here in Futing!

29:56.760 --> 29:59.280
I came to Futing to help the Miao family
out of their predicament.

30:00.000 --> 30:03.960
I'm the investor
in An Su's family shipping business.

30:04.040 --> 30:06.120
I couldn't just sit back and do nothing.

30:06.200 --> 30:09.680
What morals and obligations
outweigh propriety and decency?

30:10.200 --> 30:11.560
An unmarried young lady like you

30:11.640 --> 30:14.200
is supposed to be staying at home
preparing for marriage,

30:14.280 --> 30:15.480
This is disgraceful!

30:15.560 --> 30:19.120
The Miao family were
mere tenant farmers on an estate.

30:19.200 --> 30:20.200
Now they're merchants,

30:20.280 --> 30:22.040
a world apart from you.

30:22.120 --> 30:23.360
You don't have a friend like her.

30:23.440 --> 30:26.280
Didn't our own Dou family of
the north rise from being peddlers?

30:26.360 --> 30:28.120
Later, to establish hierarchy,

30:28.200 --> 30:29.920
we divided into the Eastern
and Western Dou branches.

30:30.480 --> 30:32.840
Should we also disown our ancestors
for their humble beginnings?

30:32.920 --> 30:36.280
You… You dare debate
family heritage with me?

30:36.360 --> 30:38.040
-You're out of line!
-Shi Shu…

30:38.120 --> 30:40.160
-Calm down, Shi Shu.
-Uncle Shi Shu,

30:40.240 --> 30:42.960
Dou Zhao contributed strategies
to resolve the maritime trade crisis.

30:43.040 --> 30:45.920
She is considered a servant
of the court. You can't hit her.

30:46.000 --> 30:47.360
Stay out of this.

30:48.240 --> 30:49.520
Ungrateful child!

30:50.200 --> 30:53.360
Do you even know your grandmother
has been sick for days because of you?

30:54.400 --> 30:55.240
What happened to Grandmother?

30:58.200 --> 30:59.160
What's wrong with her?

30:59.240 --> 31:02.160
Your grandmother fell ill
from missing you too much.

31:02.240 --> 31:03.400
Ying Xue is taking care of her now.

31:04.080 --> 31:04.960
Wang Ying Xue?

31:05.040 --> 31:07.880
You're so full of ideas and so capable.

31:08.560 --> 31:10.960
What does the death of a family member
even mean to someone like you?

31:11.040 --> 31:12.080
Uncle Shi Shu,

31:12.160 --> 31:13.640
I've learned my lesson now.

31:13.720 --> 31:15.680
Traveling to Futing was a mistake.

31:15.760 --> 31:16.840
I'll accept any punishment you see fit.

31:17.440 --> 31:20.160
Please just allow me to return
home quickly to care for Grandmother.

31:22.960 --> 31:25.600
Deliver this letter
to the local authorities

31:26.480 --> 31:28.320
and make it clear that
our family's legitimate daughter

31:28.400 --> 31:30.520
-was never in Futing.
-Got it.

31:40.440 --> 31:41.320
Father, Uncle Shi Shu,

31:42.520 --> 31:44.240
I know Grandmother's condition best.

31:44.760 --> 31:47.160
This can't be delayed.
Why don't we set out tonight?

31:47.800 --> 31:49.040
Now you feel the urgency?

31:50.320 --> 31:53.040
Your mother is looking after her now.
There's no rush.

31:53.760 --> 31:55.120
But your father and I

31:55.200 --> 31:57.840
have traveled a long way,

31:58.520 --> 32:00.160
pulling countless strings,

32:00.760 --> 32:04.720
all for the sake of protecting you.

32:06.040 --> 32:07.960
I understand completely, Uncle.

32:08.520 --> 32:12.040
I will hand over all my private assets
in Futing to the family

32:12.120 --> 32:13.280
to atone for my mistakes.

32:16.280 --> 32:17.600
What nonsense!

32:18.120 --> 32:19.880
Do you think your father and I

32:19.960 --> 32:22.160
came all this way just to
take over your meager assets?

32:22.240 --> 32:23.720
That's not what I meant.

32:24.440 --> 32:26.920
I'm willing to return home,
stay under house arrest,

32:27.000 --> 32:28.920
and fully submit to
the guidance of my elders.

32:31.120 --> 32:32.280
Shou Gu means well.

32:33.000 --> 32:35.040
Shi Shu, why don't we set out now?

32:38.800 --> 32:41.920
We've traveled far
and deserve a few days of rest.

32:42.760 --> 32:43.760
But fine.

32:44.760 --> 32:46.800
We'll rest tonight and leave at dawn.

32:47.480 --> 32:48.680
Thank you, Uncle.

33:11.640 --> 33:13.560
TEA

33:14.680 --> 33:15.520
Sir,

33:16.360 --> 33:17.320
what can I get you?

33:43.800 --> 33:45.640
We could've stayed overnight in Wu Town,

33:46.920 --> 33:48.360
but she insisted on
traveling without rest.

33:49.240 --> 33:52.120
Now we're stuck in the middle of nowhere!

33:53.480 --> 33:55.600
Shi Shu, have some water and calm down.

33:57.720 --> 34:00.240
Shou Gu is just eager
to see her grandmother.

34:00.320 --> 34:02.240
She's really worried about her.

34:03.520 --> 34:05.040
Since everyone's tired,

34:05.120 --> 34:07.280
let's set up camp here for the night.

34:10.800 --> 34:13.239
Master Shi Shu, Master Shi Ying,
there's a military camp just ahead.

34:25.199 --> 34:27.480
Are you Master Shi Shu and
Master Shi Ying from the Dou family?

34:29.360 --> 34:30.280
Yes, that's us.

34:30.800 --> 34:32.880
And how are you, sir?

34:32.960 --> 34:34.080
Greetings, my lords.

34:34.159 --> 34:35.600
We are troops stationed at the outskirts.

34:35.679 --> 34:39.080
The camp ahead is a rest area our army
has prepared for travelers on the road.

34:39.600 --> 34:41.560
You can rest there without concern.

34:42.639 --> 34:44.440
We wouldn't dare impose
on the military's duties.

34:44.520 --> 34:46.920
Serving you well is part of our duty.

34:47.520 --> 34:48.880
Food and wine will be brought shortly.

34:48.960 --> 34:50.880
Please don't refuse.

34:54.600 --> 34:57.160
-Thank you then, General.
-This way, please.

34:59.040 --> 35:00.560
You must be weary from your long journey.

35:00.640 --> 35:02.200
Thank you for your trouble.

35:02.280 --> 35:03.440
You're welcome. Enjoy.

35:09.600 --> 35:10.960
This meal is quite lavish.

35:11.720 --> 35:13.320
It's almost too lavish,

35:13.840 --> 35:15.240
not like something
a military camp would prepare.

35:15.840 --> 35:17.840
-Thank you.
-Let me fill your glass.

35:17.920 --> 35:18.960
Thank you.

35:21.720 --> 35:23.520
Young Lady, traveling in such a rush
might have upset your stomach.

35:23.600 --> 35:25.320
It's best to avoid
these heavy, greasy dishes.

35:25.400 --> 35:27.800
I'll go see if they have
some light porridge.

35:41.520 --> 35:42.560
Oh…

35:55.720 --> 35:59.280
Officer, may I know what time it is now?

35:59.880 --> 36:01.960
It's the hour of the Yin, Young Lady Zhao.

36:04.200 --> 36:05.520
Young Lady Zhao?

36:06.360 --> 36:07.720
They're Futing soldiers.

36:08.480 --> 36:09.920
If I'm not mistaken,

36:11.080 --> 36:11.920
they're the Duke of Ding's Army.

36:12.000 --> 36:14.880
What's the Duke of Ding's Army
doing in Hanzhou?

36:15.400 --> 36:16.440
I'll explain later.

36:30.400 --> 36:32.760
YUZHOU

36:34.960 --> 36:36.800
Travel permit, please.
Where are you sending these?

36:36.880 --> 36:37.960
The market.

36:38.920 --> 36:39.760
Thank you.

36:51.920 --> 36:54.840
Master Shi Ying, they say bandits
have been rampant in Yuzhou City,

36:54.920 --> 36:56.920
we need a travel permit to enter the city.

36:57.440 --> 36:58.440
We left in such a rush.

36:59.120 --> 37:00.480
We haven't prepared any travel permits.

37:00.560 --> 37:01.400
Su Lan,

37:01.920 --> 37:03.040
I bet someone has
made arrangements for us.

37:03.680 --> 37:05.080
Call Gao Sheng over.

37:07.560 --> 37:08.400
Young Lady.

37:09.400 --> 37:10.720
Tell the guards that your masters

37:10.800 --> 37:14.920
are the officials from Ministry of Rites
returning to the capital on assignment.

37:15.000 --> 37:16.120
See if that gets us through.

37:16.200 --> 37:17.760
Have you checked the goods?

37:17.840 --> 37:18.720
All good.

37:19.400 --> 37:22.040
Sir, could you allow
my master to pass first?

37:22.720 --> 37:23.960
What's your master's official position?

37:24.560 --> 37:26.480
Dou Shi Shu, an official
from the Ministry of Rites.

37:28.920 --> 37:29.760
Lord Dou from the Ministry of Rites?

37:30.520 --> 37:31.400
Yes.

37:32.600 --> 37:34.800
Clear the way! Let them through!

37:35.520 --> 37:36.560
Clear the way!

37:39.880 --> 37:41.200
When we passed through Yuzhou City before,

37:41.920 --> 37:43.600
we were never given such priority.

37:45.520 --> 37:46.960
What's going on here?

37:47.760 --> 37:48.680
My Lord,

37:48.760 --> 37:50.320
they say it was an order from above,

37:51.000 --> 37:52.960
that Lord Dou from the Ministry of Rites
is to be given priority passage.

37:53.480 --> 37:54.360
Really?

38:05.720 --> 38:06.960
Believe me,

38:07.040 --> 38:09.280
this has nothing to do with either of us.

39:00.360 --> 39:02.000
Young Lady, the wheel is stuck.

39:02.640 --> 39:03.840
Why have we stopped?

39:03.920 --> 39:06.000
Young Lady Zhao's carriage is stuck.

39:17.640 --> 39:19.680
They're coming to rob us!

39:27.960 --> 39:29.040
Shou Gu!

39:29.720 --> 39:31.120
Give me a hand here!

39:32.240 --> 39:34.680
One, two, three!

39:34.760 --> 39:36.680
One, two, three!

39:37.440 --> 39:40.080
One, two, three!

39:50.440 --> 39:51.720
Who are you?

39:52.440 --> 39:54.160
We're villagers from around here.

39:54.240 --> 39:55.160
The roads here are uneven.

39:55.240 --> 39:58.160
When it rains, carriages often get stuck.

39:58.880 --> 40:00.480
We're just here
to lend a hand pushing them out.

40:02.800 --> 40:03.800
Thank you all.

40:04.600 --> 40:08.400
Su Lan, give them some silver pieces
as a token of appreciation.

40:10.360 --> 40:12.440
We're not here for rewards, just to help.

40:12.960 --> 40:14.280
There are more of us ahead.

40:14.360 --> 40:16.200
Wishing you a safe journey,
Young Lady Zhao.

40:17.160 --> 40:19.080
-Let's go.
-Go.

40:19.160 --> 40:20.000
Let's go.

40:22.920 --> 40:24.400
How do they all know
to call you Young Lady Zhao?

40:25.120 --> 40:26.640
Don't say anything. Get in.

40:29.040 --> 40:30.320
I rarely travel far,

40:30.400 --> 40:32.920
but seeing this now,
we're really living in a time of peace.

40:33.840 --> 40:35.760
What time of peace?

40:36.320 --> 40:37.840
They're here especially for your daughter.

40:39.000 --> 40:41.480
God knows how she got involved
with those unsavory people.

40:43.840 --> 40:45.400
Young Lady Zhao is
a kind and generous person.

40:46.080 --> 40:47.720
Heaven is always looking out for her.

40:49.760 --> 40:50.680
You must be joking, Shi Shu.

40:51.560 --> 40:54.800
How could Shou Gu possibly know them?
Let's keep moving.

41:08.400 --> 41:10.440
CUI'S RESIDENCE

41:16.840 --> 41:17.840
Shou Gu.

41:19.240 --> 41:20.200
Shi Shu.

41:21.600 --> 41:23.240
Aren't you going in to visit Mother?

41:23.760 --> 41:25.120
Are you really going to the estate?

41:25.880 --> 41:27.280
What about your work at
the Ministry of Revenue?

41:27.360 --> 41:29.160
But Mother is still ill.

41:29.760 --> 41:31.240
And we're not doctors.

41:31.320 --> 41:32.720
Seeing us won't make her better.

41:33.440 --> 41:35.920
She's got Shou Gu
and Ying Xue to take care of her.

41:36.000 --> 41:37.320
Father, Uncle,

41:37.840 --> 41:39.240
I'll go see Grandmother now.

41:41.080 --> 41:42.840
Since the marriage agreement
has been signed,

41:44.000 --> 41:46.320
you should now focus on
fulfilling your duties

41:46.400 --> 41:47.600
and prepare yourself for the wedding.

41:49.320 --> 41:50.320
Marriage agreement?

41:50.840 --> 41:52.360
Didn't your father tell you?

41:52.920 --> 41:54.280
While you were in Futing,

41:54.800 --> 41:55.880
your father and mother

41:56.600 --> 41:58.040
signed the marriage agreement for you.

41:59.080 --> 42:00.000
It was a pressing matter.

42:00.640 --> 42:02.440
I wanted to discuss it
with you after you returned,

42:02.960 --> 42:06.440
but Ying Xue went ahead
and signed the agreement.

42:08.960 --> 42:09.800
Shou Gu!

42:13.080 --> 42:14.800
Dou Shi Shu and Dou Shi Ying

42:14.880 --> 42:16.560
are shallow and heartless.

42:18.200 --> 42:20.200
Unlike you, My Lord,

42:20.280 --> 42:22.120
you escorted Young Lady Zhao
all the way here

42:22.200 --> 42:23.720
without even letting her know.

42:25.680 --> 42:28.200
She made it clear
she didn't want to see me again,

42:28.880 --> 42:30.240
so there's no need to disturb her.

42:31.080 --> 42:33.480
As long as she can see
her grandmother a little sooner,

42:34.120 --> 42:35.200
that's what matters.

42:43.840 --> 42:44.760
Zhao,

42:45.360 --> 42:46.720
I'm so glad

42:46.800 --> 42:48.440
to see you home safely.

43:04.680 --> 43:07.240
Song Mo killed his father
and brother this same year.

43:07.320 --> 43:09.760
Could there be another reason,
besides avenging the Duke of Ding,

43:09.840 --> 43:11.880
that caused such a drastic change
in his character?

43:11.960 --> 43:13.600
My personal guards are in danger,

43:13.680 --> 43:15.560
and my mother has just died.

43:15.640 --> 43:17.080
I've stepped into a deadlock,

43:17.160 --> 43:18.560
and what I need now

43:19.080 --> 43:21.080
is the strength to fight.

45:09.720 --> 45:12.560
NO ANIMALS WERE HARMED
DURING THE MAKING OF THIS FILM.
